<h2><?php echo _('What is User Manager')?></h2>
<p style="width:80%"><?php echo _('FreePBX User Manager is taking the place of several modules which have attempted to create and manage user separate from Extensions, modules such as iSymphony and RestAPI are a few of these modules. Coming in FreePBX 12 the new User Control Panel will also use User Manager.')?></p>
<p style="width:80%"><?php echo _('In FreePBX User Manager you will be able to create users that have access to Extentions or Device/User Mode Users and the settings associtated with those Devices. For example, a new user could be created that can log into User Control Panel and access the voicemail of 3 other accounts.')?></p>
